                </span>
                <input type="text" placeholder="EJ: 8821" style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.75rem 1rem 0.75rem 2.75rem; background: #f2f4f6; border: none; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; outline: none; color: #191c1e;" />
