                    </td>
                    <td style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;">
                        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: #191c1e; display: block;">Eleanor Fant</span>
                        <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #3f484d;">efant@architect.io</span>
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;">
                        <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #3f484d;">24 Oct, 2023</span>
